{"tid":1574682,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢見到蟲系魔法師","createTime":"2019-09-16T14:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T11:51:58.000Z","uid":256561,"like":111,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"c868cb01d460e481aeeeab569a4b21a630a4d3d8","tid":1574682,"uid":256561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:00:58.000Z","msg":"話說果日我係富臨打打下邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打到第 4 round，個人開始飽飽地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n突然無啦啦有個盒從天而降，<br />\n一打開轟啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成大堆蝗蟲定草蜢定蟋蟀乜乜柒柒飛撚哂出黎<br />\n<br />\n嚇撚到成間店 d 人個個雞飛走狗差 d 人踩人。<br />\n個經理叫到成個肥媽咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你啊媽個閪！嚇到我鳩都縮埋。<br />\n單都無埋就走撚左。<br />\n<br />\n屌，之後疾一疾一醒，仆街原來發夢。"},{"pid":"b41748aa6e7cd254fe8415015815c3ab57d34cfb","tid":1574682,"uid":33930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:01:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日1