05:37:14.000Z","msg":"light push"},{"pid":"8c1739f74500a731f2a5908cc3c1229256123029","tid":1574682,"uid":316660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T05:41:15.000Z","msg":"油女志乃？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a563b6b66f74367148579f8ac639ed8b1837a4","tid":1574682,"uid":28031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T06:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ddc74d4d04ebe6837bcaa3facadce2389955481","tid":1574682,"uid":239492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:25:01.000Z","msg":"蟲遁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858f6bb791a7047b4a8f505a2db30bb62189a9d4","tid":1574682,"uid":256561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:08:14.000Z","msg":"pushhhh"},{"pid":"695de54cc0997c79e380b8bca475ef392003913b","tid":1574682,"uid":108687,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:11:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1629330164029830/posts/2139187066377468/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1629330164029830%2Fposts%2F2139187066377468%2F&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbeSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=840694ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1629330164029830/posts/2139187066377468/</a><br />\n<br />\nfrom GYMZACDON ：<br />\n【求下大家宣揚呢個概念】<br />\n<br />\n我不批評唱歌，因為可以保持意識形態<br />\n但如果大家將時間投放於操練、強身、健體<br />\n<br />\n其實更為有效，每日花一小時時間，做下d濕尻幾分鐘乜乜乜，落公園海旁行番30-45分鐘<br />\n<br />\n一路做一路唱，更加實際，而大家亦得到更多<br />\n<br />\n我重申一次，現在體能比一切重要，6月至今如果已經開始training<br />\n而家9月，每個新手都已經好大進步！<br />\n<br />\n起碼跑、跳、擲、避、蹲、推、拉都已經有改善<br />\n<br />\n我求下大家share出去，正視一下問題。<br />\n<br />\nWorkshop、義教我會繼續做，做到贏為止！<br />\n都好過乜都冇做！<br />\n為開心好、健康好、逃跑好、乜都好！一定有用！<br />\n<br />\n呢個概念我地一直提倡，現時社會狀況，更為適用！<br />\n亦希望大家明白有幾撚重要！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uCWYjDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuCWYjDA.jpg&h=d0a9c076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二百萬人<br />\n10%願意健身 = 20萬準戰士<br />\n就算只有1% 都 = 兩萬準戰士<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">全民健身全民健身全民健身全民健身</span>"},{"pid":"4f62ce79f229bf9cf6c7f7b8515185e8c5128b2e","tid":1574682,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T20:02:20.000Z","msg":"一睇到個經理叫到成個肥媽咁即刻有畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03621d39d3a280f0e94151223130e226295a1ba","tid":1574682,"uid":322804,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B96Bt2j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB96Bt2j.jpg&h=befb224c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔係發夢一陣入樽"},{"pid":"1d29cd24386994d270fb4d5ec68e7ab54d596865","tid":1574682,"uid":94290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5496b6bf2c55c1802858b558e02f58a4614f8051","tid":1574682,"uid":45536,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:04:53.000Z","msg":"除左曱甴呢類即時傷害<br />\n都可以暗放白蟻長期傷害"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:16:47.000Z","msg":"警察叔叔個個都要搜一搜身 真係搜到下年都未搜完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1600410\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1600410</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"58a2c4d86a78954f40717a17a7d8217d8f65d392","tid":1574682,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5496b6bf2c55c1802858b558e02f58a4614f8051","tid":1574682,"uid":45536,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:04:53.000Z","msg":"除左曱甴呢類即時傷害<br />\n都可以暗放白蟻長期傷害"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:38:12.000Z","msg":"曱甴係即時加永久<br />\n極高繁殖率 有排生成間都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}